	CDN buckets:

		- pubnub.s3.amazonaws.com
		- cdn.pubnub.com.a.prod.fastly.net

		- pubnub.zendesk.com

			- help


	Nonfunctional domains:

		- ^
		- status	(tumblr)
		- www	(interrupted)


	Problematic subdomains:

		- www.help	(dropped)


	Fully covered subdomains:

		- admin
		- (www.)help	(www â†’ ^)
		- ps\d*

